lines.text:
[having sex with the prince]
Fairy, Ah, Fairy Godmother, he gave me, Ah, snappin' pussy!
Which one of ya honkeys got my bag?

[after Cinderella dresses Stepmother, Drucella, and Marbella for the ball]
*We* should have been Charlie's Angels!

[Upon meeting Stepmother, Drucella, and Marbella]
My God, *three* flew over the cuckoo's nest!
